Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:40.87,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我能问你一件事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.10,0:13:41.72,Default JP,,0,0,0,,何？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.10,0:13:41.72,Default CN,,0,0,0,,问什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:46.17,Default JP,,0,0,0,,藤P先輩は  将来の夢ってありますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:46.17,Default CN,,0,0,0,,藤P学长 你有将来的梦想吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:50.62,Default JP,,0,0,0,,例えば  サッカー選手とか...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:50.62,Default CN,,0,0,0,,比如说 想当足球选手...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:51.67,Default JP,,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:51.67,Default CN,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:55.10,Default JP,,0,0,0,,そうだな...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:55.10,Default CN,,0,0,0,,这么说来...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:56.67,Default JP,,0,0,0,,いけ！
