Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:12.22,Monster CN,,0,0,0,,搞事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:16.70,Default JP,,0,0,0,,私達の目の前に...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:16.70,Default CN,,0,0,0,,请将希望...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:18.02,Default JP,,0,0,0,,希望を...！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:18.02,Default CN,,0,0,0,,送到我们面前吧...！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:20.72,Default JP,,0,0,0,,私達の手の中に...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:20.72,Default CN,,0,0,0,,请授予我们...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:22.62,Default JP,,0,0,0,,希望を...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:22.62,Default CN,,0,0,0,,希望的...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.17,0:18:24.82,Default JP,,0,0,0,,希望の力を！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.17,0:18:24.82,Default CN,,0,0,0,,授予我们希望的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:01.72,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ザケンナー  お前の力を見せてやれ！
